The panel contains only the list container div. The `loadDisputes()` function in `admin.js` will populate it dynamically. The existing tab-switching logic in `admin.js` (lines 13–20) already works generically via `data-tab` attributes, so no JavaScript change is needed to make the tab clickable and visible — it works automatically.

