### Overview

This change has five coordinated touch points: one backend route addition, one API client addition, two frontend file changes (HTML + JS for admin), one frontend file change (removal from claim detail), and a new integration test class. No new serializers, models, or services are needed. The work is additive everywhere except `claim-detail.js`, where two blocks are deleted.

